attributes.title: NEVER GET THIS APP
attributes.review: I got this app expecting to see people praising the Cheeto but instead when I downloaded it there was a bunch of hate for BTS on my Twitter page and I find that offending so I went to rant about it but instead when I clicked out of twitter there was a picture of the Cheeto staring at his naked daughter on my lockscreen. I was very upset to see this because I had Kim Namjoon on my lockscreen so I tried to change it to a picture of Flattykawa the door king but thenwas led to a video on my YouTube of the Cheeto being racist and sexist and that angered me because I didn’t want to look at his ugly face so I went to my fridge to get ice cream because I was sad of how bad my day has been going but when I opened my freezer, I saw a bunch of pictures of the Cheeto so I shut my freezer door as quickly as possible only to find my sleep paralysis demon chanting trump supporting words like a cult chant so I ran out of my house only to find Karen’s and Cheeto Supporters burning the LGBTQ+ flag so I ran back inside to get comfort from my cat named Min Suga but only to find that the Racists stole him and held him hostage and would only give him back if I stopped stanning BTS so I had to go onto twitter to get the Twitter kpop stans to help me hunt the people down but they hacked my twitter so all I saw was Racism and that was bad so I used another phone only to find out that they turned my family into racist Cheeto Supporters so I ran out of my house and prayed to the fuzzy worm demons and Namjesus and Asahi just so my life could become normal again but because of all the racism going around I lost my connection to the fuzzy worm demons, Namjesus, AND Asahi so I figured the only way to get my cat back, my twitter back, my freezer back, and everything else was to delete the app so luckily I did and it made everything go back to normal but I now had a bunch of Karen’s and Cheeto supporters bothering me so don’t download this app because it will make your life horrible and it will take all of your credit card info to buy LGBTQ+ flags and burn them all, and now I have no money to buy a Coach Ukai Body Pillow BEWARE OF THIS APP!!!!
